d delivered substantial growth in the college endowment through a period of rapidly changing market conditions ms mendillos background and extensive experience has enabled her to make a significant contribution to the boards oversight of gms strategic initiatives particularly the evaluation of gms disciplined capital allocation framework and its financial policies and transactions and varied financial and risk management issues source general motors company on    sign up for equilar atlas and view jane l mendillos full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like jane l mendillo more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in jane l mendillos network and community follow changes in jane l mendillos employment and moneyinmotion connect with jane l mendillo through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example jane l mendillo jane l mendillos connections  sign up now to view jane l mendillos  connections » timothy e lee former executive vice president global manufacturing  chairman gm china general motors company carol m stephenson board member general motors company sylvia jay former board member lazard ltd daniel ammann president general motors company mark l reuss executive vice president global product development purchasing and supply chain general motors company alexander f stern chief operating officer managing director global head strategy and chief executive officer financial advisory lazard ltd jaime ardila board member accenture plc theodore m solso lead independent director ball corporation james j mulva board member general electric company randall d mott board member the dun  bradstreet corporation popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thomas j lynch executive chairman te connectivity ltd john j kita evp and cfo a o smith elon r musk ceo and chairman tesla david j oconnor president and c