on and partners healthcare she is a graduate of yale college and the yale school of management and a former member of the investment committee at yale related news berklee today expanding the board of trustees berklee announces cathy young as executive director of boston conservatory at berklee berklee today scholarships investing in extraordinary students in need of support all news related events xenia karungu thursday  july     pm wakefield library olivia pérez collellmir thursday  august     pm charlestown navy yard guitar sessions benjamin verdery wednesday  august     pm boston conservatory theater all events copyright   berklee college of music contact us policies accreditation notices  disclosures careers at berklee gm jane l mendillo insider trades for general motors co bulletin investor alert new york markets close in market snapshot winners and losers expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close general motors co nyse gm go set alerts find a broker join td ameritrade market index overview profile news charts financials historical quotes analyst estimates options sec filings insiders marketstatecountryus general motors co market open  real time quotes jul    pm gm quoteszigmancomposite   change   volume volume m real time quotes quoteszigmancomposite previous close     change   day low day high    week low  week high   insider activity individual jane l mendillo ms jane l mendillo cfa mba is president  chief executive officer at harvard management co inc and president  director at blue marble holdings corp ms mendillo rejoined harvard management in july  she returned to hmc after serving as chief investment officer of wellesley college from  to  prior to wellesley she spent  years at hmc where her responsibilities included oversight of all of the portfolios outside managed assets as vice president of external management after serving as a member of the internal equity and private equity 