 leadership jane l mendillo director jane l mendillo age  has spent over  years in the fields of endowment and investment management as the ceo of the harvard management company from  to  she managed harvard university’s approximately  billion global endowment and related assets across a wide range of public and private markets ms mendillo was previously the chief investment officer at wellesley college for six years prior to that she spent  years at the harvard management company in various investment roles earlier in her career she was a management consultant at bain  co and worked at the yale investment office ms mendillo is a member of the board of directors and investment committee of the mellon foundation and the boston foundation and is on the board of directors of the berklee college of music she also chairs the investment committee of the partners healthcare system and serves as a senior investment advisor to the old mountain private trust company she is a graduate of yale college and the yale school of management ms mendillo is a member of the audit committee of the board of directors jane l mendillo cfa executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of lazard ltd snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile jane l mendillo cfaindependent director lazard ltdagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriessee board relationships background ms jane l mendillo cfa serves as a senior investment advisor to the old mountain private trust company ms mendillo served as the chief executive officer and president at harvard management company inc from july   to  and served as its vice president and director she spent  years at the harvard management company in various investment roles she served as the chief investment officer at wellesley college endowment from july   to  where  she built the colleges first investment office and restructured its investment portfolio she spent  years at hmc where her responsibilities included oversight of all of the portfolio’s outsidemanaged assets as vice president of external management after serving as a key member of the internal equity and private equity management teams she began her business career as a management consultant with bain  company inc in boston she served as the chairman and director at tiff advisory services inc she has been an independent director of lazard ltd and lazard group llc since april  she serves as a director of the boston foundation she serves as a director of the mellon foundation she served as a director of general motors company since june   until june   she serves as a member of the boston security analysts society inc the council on foreign relations the boston committee on foreign relations and the boston economic club she serves on the board of the berklee college of music she also chairs the investment committee of the partners healthcare system ms mendillo is a chartered financial analyst she earned an mba from the yale school of management and a ba from yale collegeread full background corporate headquarters clarendon househamilton  hmbermudaphone fax  board members memberships directorboston foundation thepresentindependent directorlazard ltdpresentdirectorlazard group llc education ba yale universitymba the yale school of management other affiliations harvard management company incbain  company incyale universitywellesley college endowmentboston foundation thethe yale school of managementlazard group llctiff advisory services incgeneral motors company annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation total annual cash compensationtotal calculated compensation request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloo